The Indian government has accepted
the resignation of  Anand Mahindra , managing director of  Mahindra
& Mahindra Ltd. (MM) , as an independent director of state-owned
carrier  Air India , the Press Trust of India reported, citing
unnamed officials.  To contact the reporter on this story:
